h1. ui:displayMessage

h2. Purpose

This tag renders a message for the user which has been set using the [displayMessage|Controller Methods] or
[displayFlashMessage|Controller Methods] methods in the controller.

See also [ui:message|Tags UI] for the variant that renders message text set in the GSP.

h2. Example

{code:xml}
<ui:displayMessage/>
{code}

h2. Attributes

None. Any specified are passed through to ui:message.
